---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const email = 'contact@aymericfremont.com';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Aymeric Fremont"
  description="Aymeric Fremont — designer and maker based in Nantes. Systems, craft, and conscious design."
>
  <div
    class="flex flex-col gap-10 md:gap-16 px-4 md:px-5 pt-6 pb-12 md:pb-16 w-full max-w-[1440px] mx-auto"
  >
    <p
      class="font-lausanne font-book text-[28px] leading-[32px] md:text-[48px] md:leading-[48px] tracking-[-1.5px] text-lime-11 text-balance"
    >
      Aymeric Fremont is a designer and maker based in Nantes, someone who grew
      up obsessing over systems and never really stopped.
    </p>

    <div
      class="about-placeholder w-full min-h-[200px] md:min-h-[320px] lg:min-h-[400px] rounded-sm border border-border-muted bg-placeholder"
      role="img"
      aria-label="Image placeholder"
    >
    </div>

    <section
      class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-y-2 md:gap-x-8 md:gap-y-0 w-full max-w-[900px] mx-auto"
    >
      <h2
        class="text-[24px] leading-[27px] font-regular text-lime-10 font-lausanne"
      >
        About
      </h2>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col gap-6 text-[24px] leading-[27px] font-light text-lime-11 font-lausanne"
      >
        <p>
          His practice grew out of a childhood spent in competitive gaming, a
          world of intricate systems and hidden paths where every decision was a
          chance to gain an edge.
        </p>
        <p>
          He carries that same analytical curiosity into his work today, geeking
          out on the precise logic of a grid or the way a carefully chosen
          padding value can make a digital space feel intentional and grounded.
        </p>
        <p>
          For Aymeric, design is a shared responsibility — a way of shaping
          how we move through the world — and he finds genuine joy in the craft
          of making things that are as smart as they are human.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div
      class="about-placeholder w-full min-h-[180px] md:min-h-[280px] lg:min-h-[360px] rounded-sm border border-border-muted bg-placeholder"
      role="img"
      aria-label="Image placeholder"
    >
    </div>

    <section
      class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-y-2 md:gap-x-8 md:gap-y-0 w-full max-w-[900px] mx-auto"
    >
      <h2
        class="text-[24px] leading-[27px] font-regular text-lime-10 font-lausanne"
      >
        Values
      </h2>
      <p
        class="text-[24px] leading-[27px] font-light text-lime-11 font-lausanne"
      >
        He believes that what he chooses to build should be as conscious as
        what he chooses to consume, favoring steady impact over noise. His work
        is a search for alignment — a commitment to missions that matter and
        the belief that a well-crafted tool can be a form of care.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div
      class="about-placeholder w-full min-h-[120px] md:min-h-[180px] lg:min-h-[220px] rounded-sm border border-border-muted bg-placeholder"
      role="img"
      aria-label="Image placeholder"
    >
    </div>

    <section
      class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-y-2 md:gap-x-8 md:gap-y-0 w-full max-w-[900px] mx-auto"
    >
      <h2
        class="text-[24px] leading-[27px] font-regular text-lime-10 font-lausanne"
      >
        Get in touch
      </h2>
      <p
        class="text-[24px] leading-[27px] font-light text-lime-11 font-lausanne"
      >
        If you are dreaming of a smarter way to build something that matters, he
        would love to help you find its shape. Reach him at{' '}
        <a
          class="underline decoration-from-font underline-offset-2 hover:text-lime-10 transition-colors"
          href={`mailto:${email}`}
        >
          {email}
        </a>
        .
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
